Package: rulectl
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Command-line tool for managing AI generated rules in Git repositories
 Rulectl is a simple command-line tool for managing AI generated rules in Git repositories.
 It detects Git repositories, creates and analyzes rules files, and includes smart rate
 limiting and batch processing for efficient API usage.